{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now after this memorable meeting in Berlin with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hamilton and the letter that arrived with her confirmation of her original promise on the 6th of October, four weeks later-- after this first letter arrived-- a young Jewish boy by the name of Herschel Grynszpan went to the German embassy in Paris after learning that his mother was killed after being deported by the Nazis to Poland.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went in the German embassy and shot the first German he saw, Legation Secretary vom Rath.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew by this time that the Nazis wouldn't let an opportunity like that go by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they used this to the fullest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And out of this killing-- unfortunate killing, because vom Rath was on the list of the Gestapo as an anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Vom Rath died a couple of days afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew it was now our turn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- on the 9th of November, we got a registered letter from the mayor of our city telling us that in-- in retaliation for the conspiracy of international Jewry-- and this was a typical Nazi term-- that we were, as punishment-- that we had to liquidate all remaining business organizations within the next two weeks.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my father was out of town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came back that night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he and I sat down and made plans how we could comply with this order.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after we had our meeting, I sat down at my desk and wrote a letter to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
